==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Touchdown
<hw>Touch"down`</hw> <pr>(t⟦ucr⟧ch"doun`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Football)</fld> <def>The act of touching the football down behind
the opponents' goal; also the score (6 points) resulting from such a
play.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Safety touchdown</b></col>. <cd>See under
<er>Safety</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Touchhole</ent>⟦br⟧
